{"tid":58513,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普︰賣走賓迪基因佢整爛我副眼鏡","createTime":"2016-12-29T01:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T01:44:12.000Z","uid":28309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de89a8417198d7d39df1ed90ab6509e3e0ad6280","tid":58513,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"向來幽默感豐富的利物浦領隊高普，在重提上季戲劇性擊敗諾域治一仗時笑言，前鋒賓迪基在慶祝時整爛他的眼鏡，是這位前鋒夏天被賣走的原因。<br />\n維拉拒售佐敦艾馬予畀紅軍<br />\n<br />\n紅軍在該仗憑著拉爾拉拿完場前入波，以5︰4驚險擊敗諾域治，入波後一眾球員走向高普擁在一起瘋狂慶祝，連高普的眼鏡亦整爛了。他受訪重提此事時便笑說︰「眼鏡是完全爛了，那是賓迪基做的，所以別整爛我的眼鏡否則你會被賣走！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然該仗贏得興奮，但高普不希望經常看到這些驚險比賽，尤其結局像上月作客3︰4反負般尼茅夫一役︰「因為這類比賽太刺激及令人擔憂了。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8dc0236e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"39218e9a109c44bf90758f652b5628cce6a3b5ab","tid":58513,"uid":3685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9040bb9366b665e3178a1651a2485b21824aac","tid":58513,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"BTK魔性澎湃 <img src=\"http://www.bolabanget.com/img_proxy.php?id=126256836\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bolabanget.com%2Fimg_proxy.php%3Fid%3D126256836&h=46abca35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00ab4fd909d59ff96e5711e077b75ac79f936d29","tid":58513,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTK魔性澎湃 <img src=\"http://www.bolabanget.com/img_proxy.php?id=126256836\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bolabanget.com%2Fimg_proxy.php%3Fid%3D126256836&h=46abca35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" cla